title: Washington becomes first state to adopt health data protections post-Roe
description: Gov. Jay Inslee signed a first-of-its-kind bill into law, putting limits on search engines and health trackers ability to collect and sell customers’ data

title: Video calls can spark joy. That’s true for parrots, too, study finds.
description: A new study found that pet parrots enjoy video calling each other, providing them a sense of community.

title: Why you shouldn’t tell AI chatbots your health concerns
description: AI search chatbots such as ChatGPT, Bing and Bard repeat the privacy mistakes of their predecessors — and create some new ones.
